title: [Gyldemar Forest, Cobbled Path]
description: The sound of flowing water is strong, echoing eerily against the silent oaks.  A sense of timelessness pervades the shadow-enclosed forest, seeming to shield it from change and outside influence.  A cool breeze rustles the leaf-laden branches, sending a tingle across exposed flesh.
